---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const lang = 'en';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang={lang}
  title="About Us — Detay Multimedia"
  description="Since 1997. With experience from 50+ enterprise projects including Shell, P&G, Bayer and Anadolu Group, we deliver business automation solutions."
>

  <!-- SECTION 1 — Intro -->
  <section class="section section-intro grid-bg">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label fade-in">Since 1997</span>
      <h1 class="intro-title fade-in">
        You're working with a team<br />
        that knows how to read the market.
      </h1>
      <p class="intro-body fade-in">
        Detay Multimedia was founded in 1997, when the internet
        was just entering Turkey. Back then, building enterprise
        websites was no small matter — it required large budgets,
        long projects, and serious decision-makers. Brands like
        Shell, Procter &amp; Gamble, Bayer, Anadolu Group, Efes,
        and Yeni İlaç trusted us with their work. Because they
        saw that we took it seriously.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2 — Story -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label fade-in">Why We Stopped, Why We Came Back</span>
      <h2 class="story-title fade-in">
        We left when the market cheapened.<br />
        Now we're at the start of a new cycle.
      </h2>
      <div class="story-body fade-in">
        <p>
          By the mid-2000s, building websites had become a
          commodity. Anyone could do it, prices fell, enterprise
          budgets shrank. We stepped away from that space — it
          was a rational decision.
        </p>
        <p>
          For the next 20 years we worked in digital media.
          Motoron.com.tr, Turkey's most established motorcycle
          publication, is still live today. Throughout that
          period we accumulated deep practical experience in
          content production, automation, AI tools, and digital
          operations.
        </p>
        <p>
          Now we're in business automation. And this looks a lot
          like the beginning of the 1997 cycle: technology is
          powerful, the market hasn't matured yet, enterprise
          budgets are open. Our advantage this time — we entered
          earlier, and we know exactly what we're doing.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3 — Approach -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label fade-in">Our Approach</span>
      <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Technology is a tool. Results are the goal.</h2>
      <div class="approach-grid">
        <div class="approach-card card fade-in" style="--delay:0ms">
          <h3 class="approach-card-title">We understand you first</h3>
          <p class="approach-card-text">We start by talking about the problem to solve, not the tool to use. The solution comes after.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="approach-card card fade-in" style="--delay:80ms">
          <h3 class="approach-card-title">We build and deliver</h3>
          <p class="approach-card-text">We deliver a working system, not a strategy document. Installation is complete, you start using it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="approach-card card fade-in" style="--delay:160ms">
          <h3 class="approach-card-title">We stay with you</h3>
          <p class="approach-card-text">The project doesn't end, the partnership begins. We're with you as the system grows and needs change.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 4 — Stats -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label fade-in">By the Numbers</span>
      <div class="stats-grid fade-in">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">27</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years of digital experience</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">50+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Enterprise projects</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">8</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Active sectors</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-number">1997</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Founded</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 5 — CTA -->
  <section class="section cta-section">
    <div class="container cta-inner">
      <span class="section-label fade-in">Let's Work Together</span>
      <h2 class="cta-title fade-in">
        Ready to automate<br />
        your processes?
      </h2>
      <p class="cta-sub fade-in">Let's start with a free 30-minute analysis.</p>
      <a href="/en/iletisim" class="btn btn-primary fade-in">Schedule a Demo →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* SECTION 1 — Intro */
  .section-intro {
    padding-top: clamp(5rem, 10vw, 9rem);
  }

  .intro-title {
    font-size: var(--text-h1);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 1rem 0 1.75rem;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .intro-body {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* SECTION 2 — Story */
  .story-title {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 1rem 0 2rem;
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .story-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .story-body p {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* SECTION 3 — Approach */
  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .approach-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    animation-delay: var(--delay, 0ms);
  }

  .approach-card-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .approach-card-text {
    font-size: var(--text-small);
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* SECTION 4 — Stats */
  .stats-grid {
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-3);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 2rem 3rem;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    background-color: var(--color-border);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* SECTION 5 — CTA */
  .cta-section {
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin: 1rem 0 1rem;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .cta-sub {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .approach-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .stats-grid {
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat-item {
      flex: 1 1 40%;
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    }

    .stat-divider {
      display: none;
    }

    .stats-grid .stat-item:nth-child(odd) {
      border-right: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .stats-grid .stat-item:nth-child(1),
    .stats-grid .stat-item:nth-child(2) {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .approach-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .stats-grid {
      flex-direction: column;
      flex-wrap: nowrap;
    }

    .stat-item {
      flex: none;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      border-right: none !important;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    }

    .stat-item:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }
  }
</style>
